A 26-year-old man was arrested on Wednesday in Ol Kalou on allegations of theft and impersonating a military captain.Nyandarua Central police boss Wilson Kosgei said Joseph Mwihaki, alias Captain Kinyua Joseph Mwihaki, robbed an M-Pesa shop near JM Memorial Hospital on September 3 and fled.Military police said Mwihaki is not a soldier.He will be arraigned in court for robbery, impersonation and illegal possession of military documents.